{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "615454d7f2e9bd38d13372f4", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": null, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": null, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "NTAS1", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76e4c52ffa3c944600e1"], "subjects": ["615d70f9a489afa3080ade2d"], "chapters": ["615d6ff12b295b085ab6ec0b"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [{"title": "NTA Abhyas Paper", "value": "86", "isVisible": true}], "previousYearPapers": [], "question": {"text": "In a population of 1000 individuals, 500 individuals have Aa genotype and 500 have AA genotype. What will be the proportion of a and A alleles in their gametes?", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "S820O", "text": "1 : 1", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "QQ5my", "text": "1 : 2", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "Nxl1N", "text": "1 : 3", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "I1dcK", "text": "3 : 1", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Individual with genotype Aa will produce two types of gametes in the ratio 1 : 1 (A : a) and the individual with genotype AA will produce only one type of gamete with A. Thus the proportion of alleles a and A in their gametes is 1 : 3.<br />Therefore,<br />allele A = (half of Aa + AA) = 250 + 500 = 750<br />allele a = half of Aa = 250<br />thus, a:A = 250:750 = 1:3", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["616057290283de43c87e3e1a", "616057b00283de43c87e3e20", "64d50cd33df7f4a7f3017f71", "66b79bbbd4b564dfab4f94d2", "67fa60d64468eb1307ceb0b0", "6807d392647479b8e869647c"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616025d5df15dcb57fd5eea7", "616025d6759af6d71d4cb3f5", "64eb06d33118f713ecfef13d", "66d58549a75f05ee8564f603", "67fdff3a378e1624ea7b690a",